  <brief_title>Using a Computer-assisted Prescription to Decrease Inappropriate Use of Plain Abdominal Radiography in Emergency Department</brief_title>
  <official_title>Using a Computer-assisted Prescription to Decrease Inappropriate Use of Plain Abdominal Radiography in Emergency Department</official_title>
  <sponsors>
